#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have used a burning program such as Nero under Windows, &k3b; will "
"feel quite familiar."
msgstr ""
"Če ste v sistemu Windows uporabljali program za zapisovanje, kot je Nero, se "
"bo &k3b; zdelo precej znano."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Featuring a simple, yet powerful graphical interface, &k3b; provides various "
"options for burning a CD, DVD, or BD (Blu-ray disc). Various types of "
"optical projects are supported including (but not limited to) audio and "
"data, video projects for DVD and VCD, as well as multi-session and mixed-"
"mode discs. &k3b; also has the ability to erase re-writeable media and can "
"perform more complicated tasks such as audiovisual encoding and decoding."
msgstr ""
"S preprostim, a zmogljivim grafičnim vmesnikom &k3b; ponuja različne "
"možnosti za zapisovanje CD-jev, DVD-jev ali BD-jev (disk Blu-ray). Podprte "
"so različne vrste optičnih projektov, vključno z (vendar ne omejeno zgolj "
"na) avdio in podatkovnimi, video projekti za DVD in VCD ter diski z več "
"sejami in mešanimi načini. &k3b; ima tudi možnost brisanja ponovno "
"zapisljivih medijev in lahko izvaja bolj zapletene naloge, kot je "
"avdiovizualno kodiranje in dekodiranje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pre-setup"
msgstr "Prednastavitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you run &k3b; for the first time, you may find &k3b; informing you that "
"no optical writer drivers have been found, meaning you will not be able to "
"write to any optical discs. There is no need to panic as &k3b; will open the "
"<guilabel>Permissions</guilabel> tab on the <guilabel>Programs</guilabel> "
"page of the configuration dialog, where permissions can now be changed. In "
"all modern systems optical devices belongs to a certain user group (&eg; "
"<quote>cdrom</quote>). If the current user does not belongs to this group, "
"he is offered to add himself to it on this tab."
msgstr ""
"Ko zaženete &k3b; prvič boste morda našli, da vas &k3b; obvešča, da "
"gonilniki za optični zapisovalnik niso bili najdeni, kar pomeni, da ne boste "
"mogli pisati na noben optični disk. Ni potrebe za paniko, saj bo &k3b; odprl "
"zavihek <guilabel>Dovoljenja</guilabel> na strani <guilabel>Programi</"
"guilabel> konfiguracijskega pogovornega okna, kjer lahko zdaj spremenite "
"dovoljenja. V vseh sodobnih sistemih optične naprave pripadajo določeni "
"skupini uporabnikov (&eg; <quote>cdrom</quote>). Če trenutni uporabnik ne "
"spada v to skupino, se mu ponudi, da se vanjo doda na tem zavihku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring the User Interface"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje uporabniškega vmesnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Upon starting &k3b; you are offered quick starts to the three most popular "
"processes"
msgstr ""
"Ob zagonu &k3b; na voljo vam je hiter začetek treh najbolj priljubljenih "
"postopkov"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "New Data Project"
msgstr "Novi podatkovni projekt"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "New Audio CD Project"
msgstr "Novi avdio CD projekt"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy Medium"
msgstr "Kopiraj medij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&k3b; can perform much more than these tasks though, and so you may find "
"that some of the other possibilities are just as useful to you. Take a look "
"at this list for a taste of other available functions:"
msgstr ""
"&k3b; lahko opravi veliko več kot te naloge, zato boste morda ugotovili, da "
"so nekatere druge možnosti prav tako uporabne za vas. Oglejte si ta seznam "
"za okus drugih razpoložljivih funkcij:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Perhaps a quick start for one or more of these other tasks would be useful "
"to you and so &k3b; can give you that, too. Simply right click on the "
"application desktop, and here you will see a menu for adding buttons:"
msgstr ""
"Morda bi vam bil koristen hiter začetek ene ali več teh drugih nalog in tako "
"&k3b; vam lahko da tudi to. Preprosto z desno miškino tipko kliknite namizje "
"aplikacije in tukaj boste videli meni za dodajanje gumbov:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring the internals"
msgstr "Konfiguracija notranjosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most of the default settings can simply be left alone. It is however, "
"recommended that you do take a look at the <guilabel>Advanced Settings</"
"guilabel> page. Here you can set various important settings, if required."
msgstr ""
"Večino privzetih nastavitev lahko preprosto pustite pri miru. Vseeno je "
"priporočljivo, da si ogledate stran <guilabel>Napredne nastavitve</"
"guilabel>. Tu lahko po potrebi nastavite različne pomembne nastavitve."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Use Burnfree</guilabel> should be set - it controls the burn, "
"ensuring that the buffer never gets dangerously low (which reduces the "
"quantity of bad burns)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Uporabi Burnfree</guilabel> mora biti nastavljen - nadzoruje "
"zapisovanje in zagotavlja, da medpomnilnik nikoli ne postane nevarno prazen "
"(kar zmanjša količino slabih zapisov)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "You may wish to automatically erase re-writable disks."
msgstr "Morda boste želeli samodejno izbrisati ponovno zapisljive diske."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The option <guilabel>Do not eject medium after write process</guilabel> is "
"invaluable if your drive is one that cannot be closed quickly enough for "
"<guilabel>Verify</guilabel> to happen."
msgstr ""
"Možnost <guilabel>Ne izvrzi medija po procesu zapisovanja</guilabel> je "
"neprecenljiva, če je vaš pogon tak, da ga ni mogoče dovolj hitro zapreti, da "
"bi prišlo do <guilabel>Preveri</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preparing to burn a disk"
msgstr "Priprava na zapisovanje diska"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When starting a new project, you should ensure that &k3b; has detected the "
"correct optical media, such as CD or DVD. On the status line at the bottom "
"of the screen you should see the size of disk which is currently set. If "
"this is not correct, or you require a different size, simply right-click on "
"it and set the preferred size from the provided list:"
msgstr ""
"Ko začnete nov projekt, morate zagotoviti, da je &k3b; zaznal pravilni "
"optični medij, kot je CD ali DVD. V statusni vrstici na dnu zaslona bi "
"morali videti velikost diska, ki je trenutno nastavljena. Če to ni pravilno "
"ali potrebujete drugo velikost, preprosto kliknite z desno miškino tipko in "
"nastavite želeno velikost s ponujenega seznama:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid "Now choose what is to be burnt."
msgstr "Zdaj izberite, kaj želite zapeči."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The top half of the screen is the <emphasis>source pane</emphasis>; it "
"functions like a file manager. You can choose ordinary files from mounted "
"data volumes or audio tracks from inserted audio discs. Names of audio "
"tracks are automatically read from CD-Text data, if your CD drive supports "
"reading it, or generated using <ulink url=\"http://libcddb.sourceforge.net/"
"\">CDDB</ulink>; the exact format is controlled by a button in the bottom "
"pane. If the names are incorrect or simply do not match the description of "
"the disc, you can edit them using the toolbar button. Your changes will be "
"cached locally and submitted to the master registry at <ulink url=\"http://"
"www.freedb.org/\">FreeDB</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Zgornja polovica zaslona je <emphasis>izvorno podokno</emphasis>; deluje kot "
"upravitelj datotek. Izberete lahko običajne datoteke iz nameščenih "
"podatkovnih nosilcev ali zvočne posnetke z vstavljenih zvočnih diskov. Imena "
"zvočnih posnetkov se samodejno preberejo iz podatkov CD-Text, če njihovo "
"branje podpira vaš CD-pogon, ali generirajo z <ulink url=\"http://libcddb."
"sourceforge.net/\">CDDB</ulink>; natančen format nadzirate z gumbom v "
"spodnjem podoknu. Če imena niso pravilna ali se preprosto ne ujemajo z "
"opisom diska, jih lahko uredite z gumbom v orodni vrstici. Vaše spremembe "
"bodo lokalno predpomnjene in poslane v glavni register na <ulink url="
"\"http://www.freedb.org/\">FreeDB</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the whole record is performed by the same artist, leave the track artist "
"entries blank, fill the <guilabel>Album artist</guilabel>, save to CDDB and "
"requery."
msgstr ""
"Če celoten zapis izvaja isti izvajalec, pustite vnose izvajalca skladbe "
"prazne, izpolnite polje <guilabel>Izvajalec albuma</guilabel>, shranite v "
"CDDB in ponovno poizvedite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now that you have your sources at hand, simply drag and drop the files and "
"directories you wish to burn onto the large pane to the right at the bottom; "
"this is the <emphasis>model pane</emphasis>. Behold a tree of your chosen "
"files forming to the left. Should there be some files or directories which "
"you do not want to burn, these can be easily removed from the project by "
"simply removing them from the panel at the bottom. Select the file to be "
"removed (you can control-click to select multiple ones), then choose "
"<guilabel>Remove</guilabel> from the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj, ko imate svoje vire pri roki, preprosto povlecite in spustite datoteke "
"in imenike, ki jih želite zapisati, na veliko podokno desno na dnu; to je "
"<emphasis>podokno modela</emphasis>. Poglejte drevo vaših izbranih datotek, "
"ki se oblikuje na levi. Če obstajajo datoteke ali imeniki, ki jih ne želite "
"zapisati, jih lahko preprosto odstranite iz projekta tako, da jih preprosto "
"odstranite s plošče na dnu. Izberite datoteko, ki jo želite odstraniti "
"(lahko pritisnete tipko Control in kliknete, da izberete več datotek), nato "
"pa v kontekstnem meniju izberite <guilabel>Odstrani</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you need to compress audio, create a new audio CD project, add the files "
"to be converted and press the button <guilabel>Convert Tracks</guilabel>. "
"This will not affect the contents of the CD if you decide to burn it; "
"however, you will be able to use the compressed files elsewhere. Make sure "
"the original files are lossless (<emphasis>wav</emphasis> or <emphasis>FLAC</"
"emphasis>), otherwise the result will be unsatisfactory."
msgstr ""
"Če morate stisniti zvok, ustvarite nov projekt zvočnega CD-ja, dodajte "
"datoteke za pretvorbo in pritisnite gumb <guilabel>Pretvori skladbe</"
"guilabel>. To ne bo vplivalo na vsebino CD-ja, če se ga odločite zapisati; "
"vendar pa boste lahko stisnjene datoteke uporabili drugje. Prepričajte se, "
"da so izvirne datoteke brez izgube (<emphasis>wav</emphasis> ali "
"<emphasis>FLAC</emphasis>), sicer rezultat ne bo zadovoljiv."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The top line will be the title of the disk. In many cases this will be fine, "
"but if you would like to change this to something else, simply rename it "
"using the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Zgornja vrstica bo naslov diska. V mnogih primerih bo to v redu, če pa "
"želite to spremeniti v nekaj drugega, preprosto preimenujte s kontekstnim "
"menijem."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "Final Steps"
msgstr "Zadnji koraki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "You are now ready to hit the <guilabel>Burn</guilabel> button."
msgstr "Zdaj ste pripravljeni pritisniti gumb <guilabel>Zapiši</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You will see on my screenshot that no disk was present. When you have "
"inserted the appropriate disk you will see a description of it on that line."
msgstr ""
"Na mojem posnetku zaslona boste videli, da ni bilo nobenega diska. Ko "
"vstavite ustrezen disk, boste v tej vrstici videli njegov opis."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are still one or two choices to be made. I would <emphasis>recommend</"
"emphasis> that you set <guilabel>Verify written data</guilabel>, then hit "
"the <guilabel>Save</guilabel> icon at the bottom of the screen, ensuring "
"that it becomes your personal default. For most modern drives it's safe to "
"leave mode and speed to <guilabel>Auto</guilabel>. If you may wish to burn "
"another copy of the disk at a later date, select <guilabel>Create image</"
"guilabel>, which will save having to set up the burn again. Set the number "
"of copies you want to burn, then, when you are satisfied, hit "
"<guilabel>Burn</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Obstajata še ena ali dve izbiri. <emphasis>Priporočam</emphasis>, da "
"nastavite <guilabel>Preveri zapisane podatke</guilabel>, nato pritisnete "
"ikono <guilabel>Shrani</guilabel> na dnu zaslona in zagotovite, da postane "
"vaša osebna privzeta vrednost. Za večino sodobnih pogonov je varno pustiti "
"način in hitrost na <guilabel>Samodejno</guilabel>. Če boste morda želeli "
"pozneje zapisati še eno kopijo diska, izberite <guilabel>Ustvari sliko</"
"guilabel>, s čimer vam ne bo treba znova nastavljati zapisovanja. Nastavite "
"število kopij, ki jih želite zapisati, nato pa, ko ste zadovoljni, "
"pritisnite <guilabel>Zapeci</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "Burning an Audio CD"
msgstr "Zapisovanje zvočnega CD-ja"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting an Audio CD Project"
msgstr "Zagon projekta avdio CD"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&k3b; supports a lot of audio formats and can convert them automatically for "
"you."
msgstr ""
"&k3b; podpira veliko zvočnih formatov in jih lahko samodejno pretvori "
"namesto vas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some distributions split this capability of &k3b; into a separate package, "
"&eg; on Debian and Ubuntu distributions you need to install the package "
"libk3b6-extracodecs, on openSUSE the name of the package is k3b-codecs. On "
"some distributions (&eg; Mandriva) you do not need to install any additional "
"packages."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere distribucije to zmožnost &k3b; razcepljajo v ločen paket, npr. na "
"distribucijah Debian in Ubuntu morate namestiti paket libk3b6-extracodecs, "
"na openSUSE je ime paketa k3b-codecs. Pri nekaterih distribucijah (npr. "
"Mandriva) vam ni treba namestiti dodatnih paketov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting the files"
msgstr "Izbiranje datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two ways to select the audio files you want to burn onto an audio "
"cd:"
msgstr ""
"Zvočne datoteke, ki jih želite zapisati na zvočni CD, lahko izberete na dva "
"načina:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &k3b;"
msgstr "Uporaba &k3b;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the bottom half of the &k3b; window click on <guilabel>New Audio CD "
"Project</guilabel> and select the files you want to burn."
msgstr ""
"Na spodnji polovici &k3b; kliknite na <guilabel>Nov projekt zvočnega CD-ja</"
"guilabel> in izberite datoteke, ki jih želite zapisati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively navigate in the folders panel to the location of the audio "
"files. Double click on an audio file or drag and drop selected audio files "
"into the bottom part of &k3b;'s window automatically starts a <guilabel>New "
"Audio CD Project</guilabel> with these files."
msgstr ""
"Druga možnost je, da se v plošči z mapami pomaknete do lokacije zvočnih "
"datotek. Dvoklik na zvočno datoteko ali povlecite in spustite izbrane zvočne "
"datoteke v spodnji del okna &k3b; samodejno zažene <guilabel>Novi projekt "
"zvočnega CD-ja</guilabel> s temi datotekami."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the file manager"
msgstr "Uporaba upravljalnika datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the folder containing your music files in &dolphin; or &konqueror;"
msgstr ""
"Pojdite v mapo, ki vsebuje vaše glasbene datoteke v &dolphin; ali &konqueror;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the files to burn and select <menuchoice><guimenu>Actions</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Create Audio CD with &k3b;</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"from the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Izberite datoteke, ki jih želite zapisati, in v kontekstnem meniju izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ustvari zvočni CD z &k3b;"
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit the Title Information"
msgstr "Uredi informacije o naslovu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can give the tracks titles or import those from <acronym>CDDB</acronym> "
"(a online service for track names). To do so double click on the track "
"(lower half of the window)."
msgstr ""
"Skladbam lahko daste naslove ali jih uvozite iz <acronym>CDDB</acronym> "
"(spletna storitev za imena skladb). Če želite to narediti, dvakrat kliknite "
"na skladbo (spodnja polovica okna)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "Burn the CD"
msgstr "Zapiši CD"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Insert a blanc CD-R or CD-RW disc into your CD writer and click on "
"<guilabel>Burn</guilabel>. In the upcoming dialog check if you like the "
"presets and when done click on <guilabel>Burn</guilabel>. The CD will now be "
"burned for you."
msgstr ""
"Vstavite prazen CD-R ali CD-RW disk v CD zapisovalnik in kliknite "
"<guilabel>Zapiši</guilabel>. V prihajajočem pogovornem oknu preverite, ali "
"so vam prednastavitve všeč, in ko končate, kliknite <guilabel>Zapiši</"
"guilabel>. CD bo zdaj zapisan za vas."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Credits and License"
msgstr "Zasluge in licenca"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Documentation Copyright see the UserBase <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde."
"org/index.php?title=K3b&amp;action=history\">K3b page history</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Dokumentacija Avtorske pravice glejte UserBase <ulink url=\"https://userbase."
"kde.org/index.php?title=K3b&amp;action=history\">zgodovino strani K3b</"
"ulink> ​"

#. Tag: trans_comment
